
For Distros using "systemd-networkd" service controlled by systemctl 

sudo nano /etc/systemd/network/20-static.network

add the following text : 
<<
[Match] 
name=<interface_name> // can be ens33 or wlps4 depending upon the interface you want to change the IP of 

[Network] 
Address=192.168.1.1 >> 

Save and run the following command 

ip addr show ens33 // To find the ip of the desired interface 
